{"tid":1913830,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我地見小學啲練習又悶又無聊, 整咗份用故事串連嘅英文練習俾大家免費下載","createTime":"2020-03-07T06:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T15:52:38.000Z","uid":279063,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"ef198ff8ef670a24091ddc5fca3c37cf6f5f323d","tid":1913830,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"話說我讀小學嘅時候做過本中文暑期作業<br />\n每個單元都有個故事連住, 例如解咗啲謎語就有攞到下一部分尋寶地圖嘅密碼<br />\n又有好多小學雞笑話, 一度做一度笑<br />\n大學讀完 PGDE 之後搵返呢個系列, 再查一查, 發現出份暑期作業嘅出版社已經執咗, 個作者去咗幫 Pearson 出 TSA 中文分類練習...<br />\n<br />\n我係英文人, 同朋友見到市面好多練習都係死操<br />\ngrammar 就淨係分 language item 係咁重複, 務求操到次次個小朋友啲 tense, active / passive voice 要轉啱樣, 但係就唔講幾時用先係最適合, 就算解釋都係用啲小朋友唔會明嘅方法嚟解, 好似咁:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBGqDOT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBGqDOT.png&h=5a3df030&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢個 powerpoint 係 longman 整俾一年級睇... 用小一唔識嘅字解抽象嘅 grammar 係咩玩法<br />\n<br />\n所有 language item 其實都涉及<strong>選擇</strong>, 例如幾時用咩 tense 幾時用咩 voice<br />\n例如 tense, 淨係教小朋友 simple past tense 要點轉樣, 可能最終識得串啱個字, 但係都無辦法清楚明白個 tense 係咩意思<br />\n<br />\n令小朋友 get 到嘅最佳方法就係要有 context (上文下理), <strong>俾小朋友睇到啲嘢會幾時用, 點先用得自然 </strong><br />\n而小朋友最鍾意睇, 又有 context 嘅嘢, 就係睇故仔<br />\n我地抄咗本暑期作業條橋, <strong>整咗份每 part 都由一個故事連住嘅英文練習<br />\n小朋友想追劇情就自自然會做晒</strong><br />\n成個 project 所有嘢都好初步, 淨係出咗三個單元 (我地叫 chapter)，第一個免費。copyright 啲嘢都未搞清楚，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係我地都唔介意俾人抄，最好有埋大量同產品競爭對手，因為我地想所有市面嘅教材都唔再死操，會顧及小朋友感受。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">依家上返我地 facebook page 做返簡單登記步驟就可以免費下載:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/missjaniceenglish/posts/717293048807223?__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmissjaniceenglish%2Fposts%2F717293048807223%3F__tn__%3D-R&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=8b36bdff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/missjaniceenglish/posts/717293048807223?__tn__=-R</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>練習內容一覽: </strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqz391u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpqz391u.jpg&h=ee5a0483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9P7hu1v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9P7hu1v.jpg&h=900792f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkTAgGw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkTAgGw.jpg&h=62543244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我地個 project 都好初步, 所以都想大家做完可以俾啲 feedback 我地<br />\n希望喺呢個殘酷嘅世界裡面，小朋友起碼喺童年嘅時候開心過，學到嘢，未來做啲有意義嘅事<br />\n假如你認同我地做緊嘅嘢, 就算份練習你用唔著, 都希望你可以講俾身邊嘅人知, share 呢個 idea 俾佢地, like 返我地個 facebook page<br />\n想知更多設計理念可以睇埋呢個 Medium post <a href=\"http://shorturl.at/EHKOT \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshorturl.at%2FEHKOT%20&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=3ff2b7b2\" target=\"_blank\">shorturl.at/EHKOT </a><br />\n因為想推 po 等多啲人知, 有英文嘢想問歡迎巴絲留言問我, 我會盡答"},{"pid":"ef9b179ecc15463595dd9db5cc4a16e458429013","tid":1913830,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"咁難嘅"},{"pid":"95425b32e37a46e729ef673b921921df1f7f0d13","tid":1913830,"uid":232228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"好有心 推"},{"pid":"2efe53a1331e617825ae4754b60d1834eb3e7848","tid":1913830,"uid":29726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58b92ddfc816cda6dc314854ca3ccc77970c7f0e","tid":1913830,"uid":279063,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ef9b179ecc15463595dd9db5cc4a16e458429013","tid":1913830,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"咁難嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"整嗰陣係諗住俾三年級學生做<br />\n<br />\n其實二至四年級都做得<br />\n<br />\n英文底唔夠其實六年級都做得<br />\n<br />\n都係睇點用<br />\n<br />\n你覺得應該易啲嗎"